If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : smart@statusinternationaluk.co.uk

You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. After connecting Alexa to your Maxim Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Maxim Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Maxim Smart account in our "Maxim Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some Maxim Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Maxim Smart app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Maxim Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Maxim Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Maxim Smart", and you'll be navigated to Maxim Smart login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
